<p>Contributors are persons or bodies associated with the item but not considered primary to the creation of its content. Examples of this would be performers in a band or opera, conductor, arranger, cinematographer, and choreographer. At this time this is no ability to specify a contributor as a corporate body. When possible, use the <a href="http://id.loc.gov/authorities/names.html" target="_blank">Library of Congress Name Authority File</a>.</p>
